            <title>[LU-10552] add &quot;lfs find --mindepth&quot;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10552</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;maxdepth M&lt;/tt&gt; option exists, but there is no corresponding &lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;mindepth N&lt;/tt&gt; option to find entries at &lt;tt&gt;N&lt;/tt&gt; directory levels down in the tree.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
